#
# Every PR requires approval from a listed code owner before it can be merged.
# This is enforced by the "Require review from Code Owners" branch protection
# rule on main.
#
# Format:  file_pattern  @github-username
# Later patterns override earlier ones (last match wins).
#
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

